Vulnerabilities.name: CVE-2022-22965
Vulnerabilities.description: Spring Framework RCE via Data Binding on JDK 9+
Vulnerabilities.remediation: 1. Downgrade Java to Java 8.x OR 2. Update spring to version 5.2.20+ / 5.3.18+ OR Update Tomcat to latest version
